nodes.text: Bounty Hunters 17 is the upcoming seventeenth issue of the canon comic book series Star Wars: Bounty Hunters, and is part of the Star Wars: War of the Bounty Hunters event. It will be written by Ethan Sacks, illustrated by Paolo Villanelli, and published by Marvel Comics on October 27, 2021.
